.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: corn, plum, cucumber, blueberry, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, april, january, july, december
City: rome, colone, boston, london, hannover
House: cornmaster, townhouse, cottage, futuristic, ranch-style
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, police-officer, dancer, lawyer, nurse
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating cucumber
2. the person who's birthday is in swedish is the dancer
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to london
4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating blueberry
5. the person eating plum is the person traveling to colone
6. the cottage house is the police-officer
7. the person eating pomegranate is the townhouse house
8. the person traveling to boston is in the middle
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the manager
11. the nurses is on the left or right of the townhouse house
12. the cornmaster house is the person traveling to rome
13. the person who's birthday is in january is the futuristic house
14. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person eating corn
15. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    pomegranate	|     corn	|      cucumber	|     plum	|     blueberry	|
| Birthday	|   july	|    april	|    march	|    january	|    swedish	|
| Job		|     manager	|    nurse	|     police-officer	|     lawyer	|      dancer	|
| City	|    hannover	|     london	|     boston	|    colone	|      rome	|
| House		|   townhouse	|    ranch-style	|  cottage	|    futuristic	|   cornmaster	|
